            <abstract>
                <gco:CharacterString>Stop Summary files represent average daily ridership at the stop level over the course of a sign-up period. The data is calculated from a variety of sources depending on the route and year. This data provides a basic geographic overview of SEPTA’s ridership. &#13;
These data files represent average daily fall ridership from 2014 – present. Accurate weekend data was not available until 2017 at which point SEPTA had more widespread APC coverage. No data is available from the Fall of 2020 due to the malware attack. APC data was not available for articulated vehicles and the Boulevard Direct from August 2020 through February 2022 due to the malware attack.</gco:CharacterString>
            </abstract>
